<br>
Druid, Rogue, Bard<br>
<br>
<br>
You can reverse fear kite all the way to 60.  A feared mob does not summon and as such you can even do some 50+ NPC's.<br>
<br>
Advantages:<br>
1. Good Heals, more then enough to heal up dshields and the time when fears wear off and the mob turns on you. <br>
2. Snare: duh<br>
3. All three classes can fear<br>
4. Mana Song (nuff said)<br>
5. Very well suited for PVP.  <br>
6. Mobile (ports)<br>
7. Most rogue items can be quested for outdoors.<br>
<br>
Disadvantages:<br>
1. Youll never fight a mob straight up<br>
